# Google Apps Script Web App URL (Deploy → Web app → copy URL ending in /exec).
# The script should read POST fields: email, name (optional), phone — and append to your sheet.
# After success, redirect to: https://your-domain.com/#waitlist-success (same domain as the site).
# Redeploy the site after changing this (NEXT_PUBLIC_* is baked in at build time).
NEXT_PUBLIC_WAITLIST_FORM_ACTION=
